Honored master! We will mainly popularize 10 apps in App Store as follows: Baby Panda Games For Preschool, Little Panda's Math Adventure, Kids' Good Habits & Manners, Jobs for Kids, Baby Panda’s Adventure, Baby bus Animals Farm, Baby Panda Loves Drawing, Baby Panda's Nature Exploration, Little Panda Policeman, Little Panda Mini Games. The programmer buddy with dark circles says all the products have been updated with the newest frameworks. Although I don’t get the idea of what he says , it seems to be incredible!
